Questions are in boxes of different colours. These matchthe colours in the legend to indicate which profile shouldaddress which questions. 1.Each colour is accompanied by a geometric shape. If thecanvas user is colour-blind, they can refer to shapesrather than colours. 2.Mixed-colour boxes (with no geometric shape) indicatequestions that should be addressed by all three profilestogether.3.
